{"tid":120044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【7警裁決】第六被告因本案與未婚妻分手","createTime":"2017-02-14T07:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T15:45:24.000Z","uid":48093,"like":419,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7eec94dc842e18487f8f80c23a3ece5d4e8f11","tid":120044,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T07:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170214/large/1487057035_5a4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170214%2Flarge%2F1487057035_5a4b.jpg&h=de440bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7名警員於佔領期間在添馬公園變電站暗角位置，毆打公民黨前成員曾健超，今被法官襲擊致他人受傷罪成。第六被告九龍城區刑事偵緝警員關嘉豪求情時透露，本案帶來很大壓力，最終於拍拖7年的女友兼，被告痛失所愛之餘，更因兩人合資買愛巢而出現財政糾紛，事件現仍未解決，令被告更加困擾，加上被告是家庭支柱，這次是很大的懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n7名被告依序為有組織罪案及三合會調查科總督察黃祖成（49歲）、觀塘區反黑組高級督察劉卓毅（30歲）、觀塘區反黑組警長白榮斌（43歲）、觀塘區反黑組警員劉興沛（39歲）、東九龍總區刑事總部警員陳少丹（32歲）、九龍城區刑事偵緝警員關嘉豪（33歲）及觀塘區反黑組警員黃偉豪（37歲）。"},{"pid":"0472e04c1b79ea81421ab193487103cad3ff1fa9","tid":120044,"uid":11420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"de7d806f3542d58c55e1bd283e53f13adf273ada","tid":120044,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T07:32:56.000Z","msg":"早知今日 何必當初"},{"pid":"a4c4ba4f5db6f54646133afbe6182deae6615c25","tid":120044,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T07:32:57.000Z","msg":"抵撚死 <br />\n祝全家長命百歲 百病殘身"},{"pid":"a0753ef14fcf9a79ffb2f54d7724cea5c50478c1","tid":120044,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T07:33:27.000Z","msg":"今次真係恭喜哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bade172b7447e6d75119c9c2552aeeec7077e9a2","tid":120044,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017